name: CI Global Financial Sector ETF
longDescription: The First Asset ETFs investment objective is to seek longterm total returns consisting of longterm capital appreciation and regular dividend income from an actively managed portfolio composed primarily of securities of issuers in the global financial services sector across developed and emerging markets. The First Asset ETFs investment objective is to seek longterm total returns consisting of longterm capital appreciation and regular dividend income from an actively managed portfolio composed primarily of securities of issuers in the global financial services sector across developed and emerging markets. Under normal market conditions, the First Asset ETF will invest primarily in equity and equity related securities.
